@node BLAZE "Blaze of Glory"

@{b}Blaze of Glory@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = W
Artist  = Richard Thomas

Text(UL): Target defending creature can and must block all attacking
          creatures it can legally block. For example, a normal non-flying
          target defender can and must block all normal non-flying
          attackers at once, but it cannot block any flying attackers.
          Controller of target defender may distribute damage among
          attackers as desired. Play before defense is chosen.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BLAZE}

@endnode
@node CONSE "Consecrate Land"

@{b}Consecrate Land@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = A/B/UL(U)
Type    = Enchant Land
Cost    = W
Artist  = Jeff A. Menges

Text(UL): All enchantments on target land are destroyed. Land cannot be
          destroyed or further enchanted until Consecrate Land has been
          destroyed.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/CONSE}

@endnode
